Package uk.ac.ed.inf.aqmaps.AStar

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CostFunction
    Abstract interface to be implemented by `StepCost` and `HeuristicCost`
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AStar
    Class to solve a pathfinding instance between two Points using A* search
    AStarWrapper
    Class implementing the the totality of our A* search algorithm to plot a roundtrip on a set of `vertics` by calling the AStar between every progressive pair of points
    Graph
    Graph class for A* search algorithm containing a set of `nodes` and map of `connections`
    HeuristicCost
    Class to compute the Heuristic cost to the goal point
    RouteNode
    Class to model geographical nodes on A* route kepping track of the `previous` node, `routeCost`, the cost so far & `heursticCost`, the estimated to goal node
    StepCost
    Class to model a complex step function, in our case it is constant
